'''Rafiq Baha Eddin Al-Ḥariri''' (ilul deg {{azmez|1|wamber|1944}}, deg [[Ṣayda]] – yemmut deg 14 Furar 2005, deg [[Birut]]), d argaz n yiweẓla (homme d'affaires). 

==Ḥariri ed Tsertit==

Yeqdec d Aneɣlaf Amezwaru n [[Lubnan]] seg 1992 arma d 1998, sakkin yerna yeqdec d Aneɣlaf Amezwaru seg 2000 arma d 2004. Hariri yurar ddur d ameqran deg tsertit n [[Lubnan]] n deffir n wemgaru (ṭṭrad), am wakken ay yurar daɣen dduṛ deg uɛawed n lebni n tmurt ay yenḍerren seg 15 n yiseggasen n yimenɣi. 

==Timenɣiwt-ines==

Ḥariri nɣan-t deg 2005, deg [[Birut]], deg yiwet n tenṭagt (attentat) sdat n [[Asensu St.George|usensu n St. George]]. Ɣef ljal n tmettant-nnes, [[Iɣlanen Yeddukklen]] (Nations Unies) sbedden-d [[Tanefrut Tusligt n Lubnan|Tanefrut Tusligt (Tribunal Spécial) n Lubnan]], d win ay yettuwekklen akken ad inadi deg temsat n tmenɣiwt n Ḥariri. 
Kra n yidisan nnan-d tettekka [[Surya]] deg tmenɣiwt-nnes, am wakken ay llan wid ay icikken [[Ḥizbullah]] yettekka daɣen, d acu kan, llan yidisan niḍen ay yettwalin timenɣiwt n Ḥariri ttekkant deg-s kra n tmura tutrimin (tiɣerbiyin) ay yebɣan ad d-snekrent ccwal d ameqran deg [[Lubnan]]. Lḥaṣul, timenɣiwt n Ḥariri tegla-d s yibeddilen d imeqranen deg tsertit talubnanit. D tadyant-a ay yessawḍen ɣer tmeskanin n [[Tagrawla n Yengel|Tegrawla n Yengel]] akked tuffɣa n yiserdasen isuriyen seg [[Lubnan]]. 
Memmi-s n Rafiq Ḥariri, Saɛd Ḥariri, yeqdec d Aneɣlaf Amezwaru n Lubnan gar 2009 ed 2011.

